title: Arrangers' Publishing Company - Marching Band 2010 [ALAC]

~ APC Marching Band 2010 ~ 

Exclusively Distributed by Hal Leonard Corporation.
This recording not for sale.


The CDs have been ripped losslessly using iTunes 10.4.0.80 with error correction enabled. There are no .cue files, and there are no .log files. Tdhe CDs appear flawless (I ripped them just after opening the package) and no errors occurred during ripping.
Files are tagged and include a scan of the CD case.
